	@$(CHK_DIR_EXISTS) "$(INSTALL_ROOT)src/" || $(MKDIR) "$(INSTALL_ROOT)src/"
	-$(INSTALL_FILE) "../../../Entwicklung/qbeam3d/src/$(QMAKE_TARGET)" "$(INSTALL_ROOT)src/$(QMAKE_TARGET)"
